    <bioghist id="aspace_5ae671da5c82cd6c99d876238e905e31">
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>Advertising executive who worked for a number of New York agencies, including Benton &amp;
        Bowles and McCann Erickson. Born 1927; BA Barnard College 1948; Young &amp; Rubicam:
        Television and radio writer, 1948-1952; Robert Orr &amp; Associates: Supervisor of
        Television Advertising and Programming 1952-1957; Benton &amp; Bowles: Copy Group Head
        1957-1964, Associate Director and Copy Chief 1964-1967; McCann Erickson: Vice President and
        Creative Director 1968-1985; Martin &amp; Lipton: President 1985-1990. Died 2015. Awards:
        Advertising Woman of the Year 1974, 1984; Matrix Award 1979.</p>
    </bioghist>
